Phobia reaches out above the sleeping wolf and lowers his baby onto 
her neck. He hoped she wouldn't awaken just yet. at least until his 
baby got comfortable.

"Good puppy" He thought as the baby latched onto her fur.

> Phobia approached the sleeping wolf, one of his babies in his hand.
> 
> "What do you dream when you dream a little dream." he whispered 
> looking over her relaxed body.
>
